title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - USA - Montana State Capitol
description:
In this video we will fly over the Montana State Capitol. The Montana State Capitol is the state capitol of the U.S. state of Montana that houses the Montana State Legislature which is located in the state capital of Helena at 1301 East Sixth Avenue. The building was constructed between 1896 and 1902 with wing-annexes added between 1909 and 1912.
